    * AUTHORS: Note that YH's assignment is in the mail.
    
    * README (scripts): Explain better the contents of the `scripts'
      directory.
    
    * lisp/muse-wiki.el (muse-wiki-wikiword-regexp): Split long line.

    modified files:
